headline: Unum (UNM) Q1 Earnings and Revenues Lag Estimates
summary: Unum (UNM) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -6.85% and 1.05%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
